@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Create job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java Developer",
  "company": "ABC Corp",
  "location": "Tokyo",
  "skills": ["Java", "Spring Boot"],
  "experience": 3,
  "salary": 6000000,
  "description": "Looking for backend developer",
  "postedDate": "2026-04-01"
}

### Search jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/search?q=Java&location=Tokyo&skill=Spring&minExperience=2

### Get all jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs

### Create application (MySQL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "replace-with-job-id",
  "applicantName": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "resumeLink": "https://example.com/resume/jane"
}

### List applications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/applications
